import React from 'react';
import { Navbar, Nav, Container } from "react-bootstrap";

const Navigation = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Navbar collapseOnSelect fixed='top' expand='sm' bg='dark' variant='dark'>
                <Container>
                    <Navbar.toggle aria-controls='responsive-navbar-nav' />
                    <Navbar.Collapse id='responsive-navbar-nav'>
                        <Nav>
                            <Nav.Link href="/comics">Comics</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/toys">Toys</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/tcg">TCG</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/statues">Statues</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/sportscards">Sports Cards</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/pedalcars">Pedal Cars</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/vintagead">Vintage Advertising</Nav.Link>
                        </Nav>
                    </Navbar.Collapse>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
        </>
    );
}

export default Navigation
